## Data Visualization

##### Saving multiple plots in one pdf with PyPlot

```julia
using PyCall, PyPlot
@pyimport matplotlib.backends.backend_pdf as backend_pdf

pdf_pages = backend_pdf.PdfPages("multipage_pdf.pdf")
x = collect(0:0.1:2*pi)
plot(x, sin(x))
savefig(pdf_pages, format="pdf")
close()
plot(x, cos(x))
savefig(pdf_pages, format="pdf")
close()
pdf_pages[:close]()
```